        <abstract> 
<p>Asks VOK to translate a passage from Franz Körte, <hi rend="italic">Die Streich-, Zug- oder Wander-Heuschrecke</hi> [1828], p. 33.</p>  
<p>Deplores the "fearful piece of tyranny" that is obstructing publication of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> in Russia.</p> 
